            "title": "韓股午後升幅擴大 收漲377點或6.87%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">韓股今早裂口高開後持續向好，午後升幅進一步擴大。南韓首爾綜合指數收報5872點，升377點或6.87%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/South_Korea_Samsung_Strikes_19986_source-ap__704px-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/South_Korea_Samsung_Strikes_19986_source-ap__704px-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">KOSPI 200指數期貨今早開市後不久即在升5%後啟動熔斷。重磅股三星首季業績勝預期，加上有傳該公司次季將DRAM價格再加30%，推動該股中段最多曾抽升逾9%，是推高韓股的大功臣。</p>\n</div>",
